description: The legendary place of Shalom Meshulam, which is known for its wonderous falafel balls. Was founded in 1949 by his father, presumably the first Falafellia in Jerusalem. So if you like your Tahini and a want to be served the best Falafel with a smile, this is the place to go!
A place where dreams come true.
Kadaif or Semolina, we've got both.
We help overcome poverty and capitalism alike.
Men in Black from the far east
